## Don't wait until your AC stops cooling

Srinagar summers make a working air conditioner essential. A pre-season service can prevent breakdowns when you need cooling most.

### Signs your AC needs attention

- Weak cooling or warm air
- Unusual noise or smell
- Water leakage indoors
- Higher electricity bills than usual

### What a service visit includes

Typical AC servicing covers filter cleaning, coil check, gas level inspection, and general performance testing. For repairs, book through Panun Kaergar by **phone, WhatsApp, website form, or app**.

### Same-day help

When a provider is available in your zone, same-day slots may be open. Use the booking form or WhatsApp with your address and we'll find the earliest slot.
